{"tid":450730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"萬聖節就到，有冇巴打絲打諗住去旺角西洋菜南街開萬聖節party","createTime":"2017-10-28T13:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T14:16:54.000Z","uid":20058,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb451891e662f41ea1aba331884fd916e0d308a","tid":450730,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T13:04:22.000Z","msg":"星期六晚上，當大家和朋友在旺角聚會時，你有沒有想過會在街上遇到喪屍？萬聖節還未到，喪屍團Zombie Paradise就突襲西洋菜街，大搖大擺巡遊，到處嚇人，分分鐘嚇走埋大媽，人來人往的街頭頓時成了喪屍們的舞台，大跳喪屍舞，打開今年萬聖節的序幕！這群喪屍來自五湖四海，他們本身不是專業的演員或特技化妝師，有的人本身是地盤工人、初中生，變身喪屍也全靠他們自己喜愛扮喪屍的熱情，自行研究化妝方法和喪屍造型。今次呢班手喪屍仲透露自製很多電子道具。對於這班喪屍來說，萬聖節就是他們一年一度的大解放！<br />\n攝影：梁碧玲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/129062/-%E5%96%AA%E5%B1%8D%E5%9C%8D%E5%9F%8E-%E5%9C%96%E8%BC%AF-%E8%90%AC%E8%81%96%E7%AF%80%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%95-%E5%96%AA%E5%B1%8D%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%87%BA%E6%B2%92%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F-?utm_content=buffercf6bc&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F129062%2F-%25E5%2596%25AA%25E5%25B1%258D%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%259F%258E-%25E5%259C%2596%25E8%25BC%25AF-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%2581%2596%25E7%25AF%2580%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25A4%2595-%25E5%2596%25AA%25E5%25B1%258D%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2584%258F-%3Futm_content%3Dbuffercf6bc%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=BdovVKhf2low3ZjtpD0yrdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=dc2abf0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/129062/-%E5%96%AA%E5%B1%8D%E5%9C%8D%E5%9F%8E-%E5%9C%96%E8%BC%AF-%E8%90%AC%E8%81%96%E7%AF%80%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%95-%E5%96%AA%E5%B1%8D%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%87%BA%E6%B2%92%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F-?utm_content=buffercf6bc&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定好好玩"},{"pid":"f917835639d4464e4d27d34e2eacab76708f91d3","tid":450730,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T13:27:41.000Z","msg":"然後有大媽唱&ldquo; 甜蜜蜜&rdquo;，&ldquo; 月亮代表我的心&rdquo; 祝賀萬聖節來臨"},{"pid":"99aa0dbdde9377b7674916c729f6a98319f3dade","tid":450730,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T13:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後有大媽唱&ldquo; 甜蜜蜜&rdquo;，&ldquo; 月亮代表我的心&rdquo; 祝賀萬聖節來臨</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20150831/large/1440988573_7bed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20150831%2Flarge%2F1440988573_7bed.jpg&h=cb42d318&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a12f51844f093b878f602142b6df7764ad0a7bc7","tid":450730,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>然後有大媽唱&ldquo; 甜蜜蜜&rdquo;，&ldquo; 月亮代表我的心&rdquo; 祝賀萬聖節來臨</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20150831/large/1440988573_7bed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20150831%2Flarge%2F1440988573_7bed.jpg&h=cb42d318&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59ffa746cb2dd4019b8c0e6aeb5579f6891f008","tid":450730,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0dcefa419f1689bd1f23db0ea30e74fe0df1fde","tid":450730,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f566bbdc35dd52fea001ed48d8ce089a34f500","tid":450730,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:16:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}